SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.staff_id) FROM Staff_in_Meetings AS T1 INNER JOIN Meetings AS T2 ON T1.meeting_id = T2.meeting_id WHERE T2.client_id IN (SELECT DISTINCT T3.client_id FROM Clients AS T3 WHERE T3.sic_code = '12345678901234567890123456789012')
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T2.staff_id) FROM Staff_in_Meetings AS T1 JOIN Staff AS T2 ON T1.staff_id = T2.staff_id WHERE T1.meeting_id IS NULL;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT staff_id) FROM Staff_in_Meetings WHERE staff_id NOT IN (SELECT staff_id FROM Meetings)

SELECT DISTINCT T1.client_id, T1.client_details FROM Clients AS T1 JOIN Meetings AS T2 ON T1.client_id = T2.client_id JOIN Invoices AS T3 ON T2.meeting_id = T3.invoice_id WHERE T3.client_id IS NOT NULL;
SELECT T1.client_id, T1.client_details FROM Clients AS T1 JOIN Meetings AS T2 ON T1.client_id = T2.client_id JOIN Invoices AS T3 ON T2.meeting_id = T3.invoice_id WHERE T3.client_id IS NOT NULL;
SELECT Staff.staff_id, Staff.staff_details FROM Staff WHERE Staff.staff_id IN ( SELECT Staff_id FROM Staff_in_Meetings GROUP BY Staff_id HAVING COUNT(meeting_id) >= 1 )

SELECT c.client_id, c.sic_code, c.agency_id FROM Clients c WHERE c.client_id = ( SELECT m.client_id FROM Meetings m WHERE m.client_id = c.client_id GROUP BY m.client_id HAVING COUNT(m.meeting_id) = 1 )

SELECT T1.client_id, T1.sic_code, T1.agency_id FROM Clients AS T1 JOIN Meetings AS T2 ON T1.client_id = T2.client_id JOIN Invoices AS T3 ON T2.meeting_id = T3.invoice_id JOIN Staff_in_Meetings AS T4 ON T3.invoice_id = T4.meeting_id WHERE T4.staff_id IS NOT NULL GROUP BY T1.client_id, T1.sic_code, T1.agency_id HAVING COUNT(T3.invoice_id) = 1
